    "Name": "Pythagoras PYG-C24",
    "Details": "The PYG-C24 replaces the C22's PPC with a Large Laser sourced from the Free Worlds League, adding two extra heat sinks for superior cooling across the seventeen total. The right arm carries a Medium Laser and Machine Gun while the left arm retains the Hatchet and Flamer. Center torso Paramedic Equipment and a one-ton Cargo Bay maintain the combat rescue role. Twin jump jets and a head-mounted Searchlight round out the configuration.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Improved Lifesupport</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 0.82</color></b>",
